{"tid":1183198,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雷耶斯遺孀公開信：沒有力氣說再見 爸爸我永遠愛你","createTime":"2019-06-02T17:56:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T05:35:08.000Z","uid":165817,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5906985e1a5afa7f83ff94f921cc7e0eb3872c1a","tid":1183198,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3AiS7h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3AiS7h.jpg&h=7c51ac01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/15J06sg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F15J06sg.jpg&h=fde2ff66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　我生命中的摯愛，我無法承受你離開帶給我的痛苦和孤獨，你令我失去了生存的意欲。<br />\n<br />\n　　今天，我要跟你道別了，但我沒有力氣。不過，我會盡快和你說句再見，因為我知道我們將會永遠在一起。待我生命的結束，我們會再次成為一家人。<br />\n<br />\n　　請你保佑我，因為我無法想像沒有你的生活；請你幫助我撫育我們的孩子；請你給予我力量，那些我沒有的力量。我會永遠想念你，你也會永遠活在我們的心內。<br />\n<br />\n　　你給予了我們最好的生活，也為我們留下了最美好的回憶。在 Noelia 的眼中，我彷彿看到你在望著我；在 Triana 的笑容中，我感受到你和我們一同微笑著。<br />\n<br />\n　　我愛你，我會永遠愛你，爸爸。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yFZ34dV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyFZ34dV.jpg&h=98f52170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLYcXyW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLYcXyW.jpg&h=bb33a485&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1642660d604fd592b3f4ffa21fccc1c5f82a78d8","tid":1183198,"uid":251815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134dddf60817cafac7ca6fe06cd0316a97b9a699","tid":1183198,"uid":194525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T18:02:03.000Z","msg":"Rip<img src=\"/assets/face